<refnamediv>
<refname>svstat</refname>
<refpurpose>prints the status of services monitored by <citerefentry><refentrytitle>supervise</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<cmdsynopsis>
<command>svstat</command>
<arg repeat='rep' choice='req'><replaceable>services</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection><title>Description</title>
<para>
<replaceable>services</replaceable> consists of any number of arguments, each argument naming a directory.
<command>svstat</command> prints one human-readable line for each directory, saying whether <citerefentry><refentrytitle>supervise</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry> is successfully running in that directory, and reporting the status information maintained by <citerefentry><refentrytitle>supervise</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>.
</para>
</refsection>

